{"tid":1984125,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"《蘋果日報》創辦人黎智英","createTime":"2020-04-22T09:05:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T20:05:22.000Z","uid":279927,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e4fd77e8ba5e44037f4b12bda13c99d4b2de183d","tid":1984125,"uid":279927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T09:05:03.000Z","msg":"要蘋果日報定要黄金<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o2iy1hh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo2iy1hh.png&h=c65f9426&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200422/V2ZC3AOTBQBTRZW2XLDRB25ZY4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200422%2FV2ZC3AOTBQBTRZW2XLDRB25ZY4%2F&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CqkErG%2BwP2VMcW32eObqVUU%3D&h=3a8fc82f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200422%2FV2ZC3AOTBQBTRZW2XLDRB25ZY4%2F&h=91b8a754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200422/V2ZC3AOTBQBTRZW2XLDRB25ZY4/</a><br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》面對廣告打壓，疫情導致社會經濟不景，並導致訂閱人數下降，加上新聞及言論自由日漸收窄，我們面臨巨大挑戰，創辦人黎智英坦言：「我哋《蘋果日報》實在經營非常困難！」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【1-Click搞掂】新增App內訂閱 輕鬆盡覽《蘋果動新聞》<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果日報》創辦人黎智英致讀者<br />\n<br />\n各位讀者你好，<br />\n<br />\n我想對你們有少許請求，《蘋果日報》實在經營非常困難！<br />\n<br />\n我首先想多謝演藝界的朋友、文化界的同行朋友，以及一些社會精英和KOL，在這段時間幫我們很大的忙，為我們發聲支持我們，先多謝你們！<br />\n<br />\n這幾年虧蝕都很嚴重，現在的情形比以前更差，受疫情影響，我們的報紙差不多沒有廣告。以前面對廣告封殺，廣告都已經減少很多，現在完全差不多沒有了。訂閱人數亦比以前少很多，從80萬跌到現在不足60萬，導致我們經營非常困難！<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200422/V2ZC3AOTBQBTRZW2XLDRB25ZY4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200422%2FV2ZC3AOTBQBTRZW2XLDRB25ZY4%2F&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CqkErG%2BwP2VMcW32eObqVUU%3D&h=3a8fc82f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200422%2FV2ZC3AOTBQBTRZW2XLDRB25ZY4%2F&h=91b8a754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200422/V2ZC3AOTBQBTRZW2XLDRB25ZY4/</a><br />\n<br />\n現在我本人已經墊支了5億5千萬來支撐着，如果真是繼續困難，我們都會撐下去，因為無辦法，我們明白這是對社會的責任，但希望你們能夠了解我們的辛苦和困難，多多幫忙，支持我們訂閱，好讓我們能夠繼續撐下去。<br />\n<br />\n以前沒有提供App內訂閱，造成很多想訂閱的人訂閱不了，因為太困難，而且有人訂閱後亦出現問題，這方面我覺得我們是有錯誤。現在開始就可以在App內訂閱，只要按「我要訂閱」，大概10秒鐘便能成功。希望你們能夠更方便地支持我們，幫助我們，謝謝！<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果日報》創辦人黎智英<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200422/V2ZC3AOTBQBTRZW2XLDRB25ZY4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200422%2FV2ZC3AOTBQBTRZW2XLDRB25ZY4%2F&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CqkErG%2BwP2VMcW32eObqVUU%3D&h=3a8fc82f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200422%2FV2ZC3AOTBQBTRZW2XLDRB25ZY4%2F&h=91b8a754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200422/V2ZC3AOTBQBTRZW2XLDRB25ZY4/</a>"},{"pid":"896ddaf82efedae67ba317ce4babccfe224543fc","tid":1984125,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T09:14:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b08d87d893f787e7f50310075252cb093b880bcf","tid":1984125,"uid":38737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T09:15:04.000Z","msg":"個topic jm9"},{"pid":"d7632e519b2ee849da00b08b88b1834b69f380a1","tid":1984125,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T09:15:28.000Z","msg":"開條課金link 啦"},{"pid":"017debc3d0463bd25e91ec46a4373ac28aafd558","tid":1984125,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7632e519b2ee849da00b08b88b1834b69f380a1","tid":1984125,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T09:15:28.000Z","msg":"開條課金link 啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T09:21:24.000Z","msg":"可以in app purchase啦"},{"pid":"f048fe852563382d3b48c495ca98f4c84dfa631a","tid":1984125,"uid":124983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T09:24:47.000Z","msg":"搵美國老友幫幫手<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e7207